\id JAS - Makua Bible Version
\h Nayakhobo
\toc1 Iwarakha ilhepiye ni Nayakhobo
\toc2 Nayakhobo
\toc3 Nayak
\mt2 Iwarakha ilhepiye ni
\mt1 Nayakhobo
\imt1 Malhove o uholhelha
\ip Iwarakha ilhepiye ni Nayakhobo ilha yaalhepiye ni ntu mmoka ehaniya Yakhobo. Yoyo ntu uyo veekinaka aari phi Yakhobo nhima awe Yesu, aari phi nholhelhi o nlhoko wa attu anrumelhenlhe Kuristo o pachapacha ni mmoka o nlhoko wa ashulhupalhe o ipuwa yo Uyerusalemu (Mitk nlhako wo 15:13). Akarumiya Napaolo ni ayo tho ahomwiihana yoyo ntu uyo “nipoto” no nlhoko wa attu anrumelhenlhe Kuristo mu iwarakha wa Agalatiya (Agal nlhako wo 2:9). Attu o ushoma anorumelhelhacha wiira iwarakha i Nayakhobo yaalhepiye iyaakha yo 50 baada yo uyaria wa Kuristo. Ni ukhalhawaya Nayakhobo phi aari nholhelhi o nlhoko wa attu anrumelhenlhe Kuristo o Uyerusalemu, veekinaka yaalhempe ikatema vaari aya akhalhaka wowo.
\ip Nayakhobo ayo anolhepa iwarakha aya iyo urwaa wa attu o “makosho khumi ni melhi amwareelhe velhaponi va” (nlhako wo 1:1). Meettuchiho anopattiya nkitabuni mu Nayakhobo ahorera wiittuchiya ni attu o nlhoko unrumelhenlhe Kuristo onkhaye nansho nlhove ninoromolha, “makosho khumi ni melhi” ninooniha mwaari wiira Nayakhobo yaalhempe aachaka Ayahudi anrumelhenlhe Kuristo. Ukhalhawaya ilha iwarakha ilha yaalhakelhiye wiira yashomiye ni nlhoko mulhupalhe wa attu, nhina mmo ihohimiacha chittu chinchi. Nayakhobo anowehaweha mwaha wo unlhoko unaacha upisha nrima ni mitheko. Upisha nrima wo ikekhiaye unoonihiya wo uvara mitheko (nlhako wo 2:17). Tho, anaamuka mwaha wo ulhohiya chinene attu o nhakhu (nlhako wo 2:1-4) ni unihimiachera wiira niweheke rata chittu chinoolhumacha ihu (nlhako wo 3:1-12).
\iot Chiri nhina
\io1 Nayakhobo anowaashikuria attu anoshoma iwarakha aya (nlhako wo 1:1).
\io1 Tho, anowaahelha nrima attu o nlhoko unrumelhenlhe Kuristo wiira avilhelheke vanohuva aya (nlhako wo 1:2-27).
\io1 Thothoni tho, anohimia wiira upisha nrima woonihiyeke wo mitheko (nlhako wo 2:1-26).
\io1 Baada yo vavawo, anohimia Malhove chiri aya ni machiri (nlhako wo 3:1-12).
\io1 Nayakhobo tho, anoohimia Irusho cha Nlhuku chihinolhikaana aya ni irusho cha attu (nlhako wo 3:13-4:10).
\io1 Anowaamuka attu anoshoma iwarakha aya, wiira ahikhalhe ni nrima wo wiifuna (nlhako wo 4:11-5:6).
\io1 Nayakhobo anomalhiha iwarakha aya wo uhimiacha ikano cho umalhihera (nlhako wo 5:7-20).
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Mii Yakhobo, karumiya a Nlhuku ni karumiya a Athithi Yesu Kuristo.
\p Kinoowiiha isalamu uwaninyu mwaatti makosho khumi ni melhi amwarelhe velhaponi vonkhaye.
\s1 Nrima ni Irusho
\p 
\v 2 Ashilhoko aka, nteelhiyeke vanolhikachiya inyu wo kila iphiro,
\v 3 ukhalhawaya nhochuwelha wiira nrima inyu walhikachiyaka phi nooria inyu uvilhelha.
\v 4 Nansho nkhalheke ni ikekhiaye wiira uvilhelha winyu unoworihani uhikhwa nrima, wiira ntimire ni ukhomalha mpaka umalhelha nhiwukuwelhiyaka ittu.
\p 
\v 5 Nansho mmoka inyu awukuwelhiyaka irusho anlhepelheke Nlhuku nommaha, ukhalhawaya Nlhuku phi naavaha attu onkhaye wo winchiva ni wo urera nrima.
\v 6 Nansho alhapelheke wo nrima wo urumelhelha ni uhichukulha. Ukhalhawaya ntu o uchukulhacha ri thoko mawimbi o bahari anokakhiya ni uveverushiya ni iphioo uno ni uno.
\v 7 Ntu thoko yoyo haanyihere wiira noopochera ittu iriyoothe wa Athithi.
\v 8 Ukhalhawaya ntu o mirima miilhi, khanooria wiitawara mmakhalhelhoni mwawe mwonkhaye.
\s1 Nhakhu ni uhikhalha ni ittu
\p 
\v 9 Nlhoko ihu nonrumelhelha Kuristo hirina ittu ateelhiyeke Nlhuku vanommwelhiha awe,
\v 10 ni munnihu ntu o nhakhu nrumelhenlhe Kuristo ni uyo ateelhiyeke Nlhuku vanonkurusha awe. Ukhalhawaya attu o nhakhu anowa umora thoko ituva.
\v 11 Ukhalhawaya nchuwa vanopharelha aya ni uviha ninoopaha minyepu, ituva chinoonyaalha ni umora ni urera waya wonkhaye unoomalha. Phi chiichammo etu, attu o upuha anoonyalha thoko ituva mu upuhani mwaya.
\s1 Uphimiya ni ulhikachiya
\p 
\v 12 Horeeriya ntu o uvilhelha vanolhikachiya awe, ukhalhawaya avilhelhaka ulhikachiya, nowa uttukiya mphumburu wo ukumi Nlhuku alhehilhe awe attu anonttuna.
\v 13 Ntu vanolhikachiyaka awe hiire, “Nlhuku phi nokilhikacha!” Ukhalhawaya Nlhuku khanolhikachiya wo uwonya mena khanonlhikacha ntu riyoothe wo uwonya.
\v 14 Nansho kila ntu nolhikachiya ni uthepiachiya wo nrima awe wo uhilhoka vanopurulhiya awe ni uwaya mu uwonyani.
\v 15 Nrima wo uhilhoka uyo wakhomaalhaka phi nowiiha milhatu cho uwonya ni uwonya uwo wakhomaalhaka, phi nommwiiha nookhwa.
\p 
\v 16 Ashilhoko aka nhithepiachiye!
\v 17 Kila izawadi yoombone inokumihiya ni kila ittu izawadi inokumihiya inatiminre inokhuma uchulhu wa Nlhuku oopilhe nchuwa ni mweeri ni ittotwa chinomwalhia wiirimu. Nlhuku hinorukunuwa mena upitikuwacha thoko mittuuchi.
\v 18 Wo uttuna wawe mwanene ahoniyara hii wo nlhove nawe ne ikeekhene nikhalhe o upacha munlhokoni mwo chittu chawe chonkhaye chuupiye.
\s1 Wiiwa ni Upanga
\p 
\v 19 Ashilhoko aka nchuwelheke yayo. Kila ntu aalhuweke wiiwa nansho apicheke wulhumacha ni tho apicheke uthunalha.
\v 20 Ukhalhawaya ntu o uthunalha khanooria ukhalha makhalhelho o upanga chittu chinothanana awe Nlhuku.
\v 21 Paahi etu nhiyeke iphiro cho uhilhokalhoka ni uwonya uriwoothe. Mpochereke wo wiitimarikha nlhove naalhiye munrimani mwinyu ninooria uwoopolhani.
\p 
\v 22 Paahi etu, mpangelheke mitheko malhove aneewa inyu ayo, nhikhalhe attu o wiiwelhelha nlhove vekha ayaru, ni wiithepia mwaashineneru.
\v 23 Ukhalhawaya ntu neewa nlhove vekha aya hoonihaka mitheko, yoyo nolhikaana ni ntu neeweha ikhove awe vakiooni.
\v 24 Ukhalhawaya vavawo nowiichoona, nansho athamaka noolhiyalha ikhove awe chiri aya.
\v 25 Nansho ntu nohelhelha malhehero atiminre anoopolha attu, ntu nothepa uvarechesha, hikhalhaka ntu o wiiwelhelha ni ulhiyalha, nansho nokhalha ntu o upangelha mitheko, yoyo Nlhuku nommaha ibarakha ni ummaha mpuha wo mitheko chonkhaye chinopanga awe.
\p 
\v 26 Ntu echoonaka wiira hochuwelha unthimicha Nlhuku, aahitawareke nlhimi nawe, nothepiacha nrima awe mwanene, uthimicha wawe uwo khunokhalha ittu. Ukhalhawaya khanonthimicha Nlhuku.
\v 27 Iphiro yo unthimicha Nlhuku Athumwanihu iri yorera ihiri ni milhatu cho unanara mmiholho wawe phi ilha, Waalhoha ashaana akhwelhiye ni manyanaangoro aya, ni waalhoha anankhwelhi mu uhuvani mwaya ni wiichinanelha mwanene wiira hinanarihiye ni chittu cho uhilhokalhoka cho velhaponi va.
\c 2
\s1 Waamukiya mwaha wo unyaraphana
\p 
\v 1 Ashilhoko aka, mwaarumelhelhaka Athithi Yesu Kuristo, Athithi o nthimicho, nhaanyaraphe attu.
\v 2 Ukhalhawaya awaaka ntu nawanre ikuwo chorera ni ipete yo idhahabu nnikokhoni mwawe u inupa inyu yo unlhapelha Nlhuku, ni vavawo nkaawa ntu hirina ittu mwommo nawanre matapwata,
\v 3 mwanlhohaka ntu warenlhe ulhe ni umwiirelha, Kharibu nkhalheke va varenreva ni vavawo mmwiirelhaka ntu nshikini uyo, Mweemelheke uwo ama mwiiraka nkhalheke vathi vawo,
\v 4 chani vavawo khannoona wiira nhonyarapha? Chani khannochuwelha vavawo wiira khannohukumulha wo uholhelhiya ni nrima wo uhilhoka?
\p 
\v 5 Ashilhoko aka, nkakiiweni! Chani Nlhuku kaathanlhe attu ahirina ittu o velhaponi va wiira akhalhe phi attu o nhakhu wo mupishani nrima anohalha upochera Imwene ilhehiye attu anonttuna.
\v 6 Nansho mwaatti khannaalhoha attu ahirina ittu. Anaa attu o nhakhu kahiwe phi yayo anowoonelhani mwaatti ayo, kahii phi yayo anouhukumulhani ayo?
\v 7 Ni ayo kahiwe phi ayo anoruwana nchina ninyu no nthimicho na Kuristo nneehanelhiya inyu nno?
\p 
\v 8 Nansho mwavarecheshaka malhehero o Imwene ya Nlhuku ihimiye ni Malhove Matakatifu aneera, “Mwaattuneke amwatamana inyu thoko chineettuna inyu mwaanene.” Wo ikekhiaye, vavawo nnoopanga ittu yoombone.
\v 9 Nansho mwaanyaraphaka nhowonya, Malhehero anouhukumulhani wiira nhotteka.
\v 10 Ukhalhawaya ntu awonyaka ata nlhove nimoka nhina Malhehero a Nlhuku, howonya Ikekhia yonkhaye.
\v 11 Ukhalhawaya yoyo eerilhe “Nhilhavelhave” uyo, phi yoyo enre, “Nhiive.” Paahi etu inakhalhaka khannolhavalhava nansho nheeva, nhowonya Malhehero onkhaye.
\v 12 Paahi etu mulhumacheke ni waaweha attu thoko attu anohalha uhukumulhiya ni Malhehero anooria unihiyerera.
\v 13 Nlhuku khanowa aamwonelha ikiriri ntu hirina ikiriri. Nansho attu o ikiriri khanoova uhukumulhiya ni Nlhuku, ukhalhawaya ikiriri ya Nlhuku inoopwaha ihukumu.
\s1 Upisha nrima ni Mitheko
\p 
\v 14 Ashilhoko aka, inoreerani ntu vaneera awe noopisha nrima nansho hoonihaka wo mitheko choombone? Chani yoyo nrima uyo unowa umoopolha?
\v 15 Ikhalhe wiira haawo munnihu mmoka ama mwanrokorihu mmoka noowolhiya ithalha ama hothalhelhiya.
\v 16 Vanorera chani weerelha yayo, “Nlhuku ovaherekeni! Nrweeke wo mpuha mwootteke mooro, mwalhieke nnoowona, wo uhimmaha ittu iriyoothe yo unkavihera mwiiruttuni mwawe?”
\v 17 Paahi etu upisha nrima vekha aya wo uhooniha mitheko yoyo uhokhwa.
\p 
\v 18 Nansho ntu nowooria wiira, “Inyu nhanaa nrima, ni mii kihanaa mitheko.” Eiyo nkooniheke etu nrima inyu uhiri ni ntheko uyo, ni mii kinowoonihani nrima wo mitheko chaka.
\v 19 Inyu nnorumelhelha wiira Nlhuku ri mmoka tu. Aye! Nansho ata mashoka o unanara ni chiyo chinomoova yoyo ni unthukumelha.
\v 20 Nhopwapwa inyu! Chani mwoonihiyeke wiira nrima wo uhikhalha mitheko uhokhwa?
\v 21 Apwiiya Aburahimu aalhakelhelhiye chani wiira ahovarechesha ikekhia mmiholho wa Nlhuku? Wo nlhatu wo mitheko chaya vankuminhe aya isadaka yo upahiya mwaamwanaya Isaka vamadhubahuni vo ukumiheriya isadaka.
\v 22 Paahi etu mwooneke vavawo wiira upisha nrima waya wahoonia wo mitheko chaya ni vavawo nrima uyo wahokhomaalhihiya.
\v 23 Paahi Malhove Matakatifu yahotimira venre aya, “Aburahimu ahonrumelhelha Nlhuku. Ni wo nrima waya ahoonia wiira ahopanga chittu chinothanana awe Nlhuku.” Nkayeehaniya ampwana awe Nlhuku.
\v 24 Haya etu nchuwelheke wiira ntu naalhakelhiya wiira hovarechesha ikekhia mmiholho wa Nlhuku wo mitheko chawe kuhii wo upisha nrima vekha ayaru.
\p 
\v 25 Yaari thoko chiichammo wa Narahabu, nthiyana o ulhavalhava ulhe. Ahaalhakelhelhiya wiira ahovarechesha ikekhia mmiholho wa Nlhuku wo nlhatu wo mitheko chawe, vaapochenre awe akarumiya o uhotelha aakihaka wo waaviriha iphiro chikina.
\p 
\v 26 Paahi etu thoko vari aya iruttu ihimmumulha ihokhwa, phiri aya chiichammo nrima uhinooniha mitheko uhokhwa.
\c 3
\s1 Nlhimi
\p 
\v 1 Ashilhoko aka, nhihuvelhe ukhalha owiittuchiha enchi munlhokoni mwinyu. Nchuwelheke wiira hii owiittuchiha va ninowa uhukumulhiya wo uweria chinene waapwaha attu akina ayo.
\v 2 Ukhalhawaya hii onkhaye va phi attu ninokwakwathuwa wo iphiro chinchi. Nansho ntu hinotteka wo nulhumo nawe, yoyo horeeriya wo kila ittu, nowooria utawara iruttu awe yonkhaye.
\v 3 Mwooneke, wiira ninowaattuka ifarasi uwano ikipande yo yuuma ittukiye mikhoyi wiira chiniiwelhelhe noorie urukunusha iruttu chaya ni waarweha uriwoothe unothanana ihu.
\v 4 Tho, mwooneke ikalhava chineera aya. Inonnuwaka chani ni weeta chikakhiyaka ni iphioo yo machiri, chinookolhelhiya iphiro wo mpondo mwankani unovara awe ntu neetiha uyo wookolha urweha unothanana awe.
\v 5 Nlhimi ninno chiicho, itturi ikaani mwiiruttuni, nansho ninowiishipa wo upanga chittu chulhupalhe.
\p Mooro chiicho, mwooneke, unakhalha vakani, unowooria upaha ithuphi yuulhupalhe chinene!
\v 6 Nlhimi ninno chiicho niri thoko mooro. Itturi ikani mwiilhaponi iri mwiiruttuni mwihu, ichanre milhatu cho uwonya, inoninanariha iruttu yonkhaye ni unipaha mooro ukumi ihu wonkhaye. Ukhalhawaya unoparihelhiya ni mooro unokhuma Ujehannamu unenene.
\p 
\v 7 Ntu nowooria waahuwa ashinama o kila nikosho. Nowooria waahuwa ashinama o umwiini, waahuwa ashinuni, waahuwa anaakoko ni waahuwa ashinama o mmashini.
\v 8 Nansho khaawo ntu nooria uhuwa nlhimi, ukhalhawaya nlhimi niri no uwonya uhintawaria, nihochara uhapalha uneeva.
\v 9 Wo nlhimi ninontotopelha Nlhuku Athumwanihu. Ni wo nlhimi nenno ninowaalhava attu yuupiye wo ikhove ya Nlhuku.
\v 10 Ashilhoko aka khavanorera mmalhakuni nkhume malhove o waatotopelha attu moombone ni malhove o waalhava attu. Ashilhoko aka uwaninyu mwaatti ihikhalhe chiicho.
\v 11 Chani nrapo nimoka ninowooria uthekhuma maashi o uririya ni maashi o maakha?
\v 12 Ashilhoko aka, chani mwembe unowooria wimma ikokho? Ama nzabibu unowooria uyara ittini? Khavanooria! Chiichammo etu nrapo no maashi o maakha khaninthekhuma maashi o uririya.
\s1 Irusho cho ukhuma wa Nlhuku
\p 
\v 13 Chani mpani ri ni irusho ni o uchuwelha munlhokoni mwinyu? Paahi etu ooniheke chechiyo wo meetelho oombone ni wo mitheko chorera chinopangia wo wiitimarikha ni wo irusho.
\v 14 Nansho mwakhalhaka ni nrima uchanre ihache ni ichimwa ni wiichoona, nhilhikache ukhuneelha ikeekhene wo wiititihachera irusho chinyu.
\v 15 Irusho thoko chechiyo khachinokhuma wiirimu nansho cha attu o mwiilhaponi momu, khachihii cho Iphumu ya Nlhuku, chinokhuma wa Nakare.
\v 16 Ukhalhawaya varii ihache ni wiichoona, vavawo vahochara injarare ni kila mitheko cho uwonya.
\v 17 Nansho irusho chinokhuma wiirimu, chiri chorera, tho chinottuna mpuha, tho cho wiitimarikha, tho cho ikiriri ni cho uwiiha mitheko choombone. Khachinanarilhe nrima mena khachiri cho nrima wo unafiki.
\v 18 Attu anaalha mu ikekhiani, anokhungura chittu cho mu mumpuhani.
\c 4
\s1 Wiichaatameriha wa Nlhuku
\p 
\v 1 Anaa indewo ni uhiiwananiya munlhokoni mwinyu mmo chinokhuma vayi? Chani khachimmwiihiya ni itama inoothemwihani mwiiruttuni mwinyu iyo?
\v 2 Nnoothanana upatta ittu, nansho ukhalhawaya khannopatta, paahi etu nnowiiva ni woona ihache. Phi naatakana inyu indewo nansho khannopatta ittu inothanana inyu ukhalhawaya khannonlhepelha Nlhuku.
\v 3 Vanonlhepelha inyu Nlhuku vawo khannopatta ukhalhawaya nnolhepelha wo nrima wo uhilhoka. Nnolhepelha wiira mmwonihiye itama chinyu.
\v 4 Inyu mwaati o ulhuva va! Khanchuwenlhe wiira uttuna chittu cho mwiilhaponi mu phi wiipanga amalhaponi a Nlhuku? Paahi etu ntu nottuna chittu cho mwiilhaponi yoyo heepanga mmalhaponi a Nlhuku.
\v 5 Paahi etu nhaanyihere wiira Malhove Matakatifu anoolhumacha malhove o uhikhalha maana vaneera aya, “Nlhuku nowoona ihache chinene wo Iphumu yenshe awe mwiiruttuni mwihu.”
\v 6 Nansho Nlhuku honivaha nnema mulhupalhe chinene, thoko chilhepiye aya wiira, “Nlhuku nowaavenga attu o mahuchuru, nansho nowaavaha nnema mulhupalhe attu o wiitimarikha.”
\p 
\v 7 Paahi etu mmwiiwelhelheke Nlhuku. Munvingeke Nakare ni uyo nowuttawani.
\v 8 Mmwaatamerieke Nlhuku ni uyo nowaatameriani. Mwiihapiheke mathatha inyu, mwaatti o uwonya va! Nkwecheke mirima chinyu, mwaatti o mirima miilhi va!
\v 9 Nchukulheke, munlheke ni wiichunlhelha. Uthiaa winyu uthathuweke nunlhiho ni mpuha winyu uthathuweke ukhalha wiichunlhelha.
\v 10 Nkhalheke wo wiitimarikha mmiholho wa Athithi, ni ayo anoutheeshani.
\s1 Waamukiya mwaha wo waahukumulha akina
\p 
\v 11 Ashilhoko aka, nhootheriane mwaashineneru. Nomwootheria ama unhukumulha nhima awe, yoyo hootheria ni uhukumulha Ikekhia ya Nlhuku. Nansho mwahukumulhaka Malhehero, paahi inyuva vavawo khannovara ikekhia, nnowiira uhukumulha.
\v 12 Nlhuku vekha awe phi neemesha Ikekhia ni uhukumulha. Vekha awe phi noopolha ni wiiva. Vano inyu phi apani nnaahukumulha akhunaninyuva?
\s1 Nhichaalhakelhe wo nlhatu no meelho
\p 
\v 13 Paahi nkiiwelhelheke vano, mwaatti nneera, “Lhelho ama meelho ninoorwaa ilha iwani ilha ama ikina, nirwee nakhalheke wowo iyaakha imoka, napange maronda ni upatta ifaida.”
\v 14 Mwaatti khanchuwenlhe chinohalha aya ukhalha meelho! Ukhalhawaya mwaatti nri thoko ittapwe inoonia wo ikatema ikhuvi nansho kaanyuma inoowalhawalha.
\v 15 Mwaatti nnophavelhiya wiira, “Nlhuku Athithi attunaka, ninookhalha akumi ni upanga ilha ni ilha.”
\v 16 Nansho mwaatti vano nnowiishipa ni wiichoona. Wowo wiititihacha wonkhaye uwo uri wo uhilhoka.
\p 
\v 17 Paahi etu, ntu chuwenlhe upanga morera nansho hipangaka, yoyo howonya.
\c 5
\s1 Waamukiya attu o nhakhu
\p 
\v 1 Vano etu, nkakiiweni mwaatti attu o nhakhuva! Munlheke ni wiichukulhelha wo nlhatu wo uhuva unowa uri mmiholho winyu.
\v 2 Nhakhu inyu uhoonta ni ikuwo chinyu chihovariya ikutihi.
\v 3 Idhahabu ni nchurukhu winyu chiholhiya nrenje. Ni nenno nrenje nno phi nohalha uhimiecheshani milhatu ni upaha iruttu chinyu thoko mooro. Nheeshungera nhakhu wo mahuku o umalhelha alha.
\v 4 Nkeewani! Khamwalhivilhe anamitheko avanre mitheko mmamatani mwinyu. Nkeewelhelhani chineera aya wo wunlha chiyo! Ikutto chaya chihaaphiyelha Athithi o Ikuru!
\v 5 Nhokhalha mwiilhaponi wo wiiphwacha ni wiiteelhiha chinene. Nhoneneviha mirima chinyu ni ukhalha thoko mwannama noweherera nihuku no uhithiya.
\v 6 Nhonhukumulha ntu e ikekhiaye ni umwiiva ntu huwirinheni ittu.
\s1 Uvilhelha mu uhuvani
\p 
\v 7 Paahi etu ashilhoko aka, nvilhelheke mpaka nihuku no uhokolhia Athithi. Mmwooneke namalhima chinoweherera awe cholhia mmatani mwawe wiira chikhomaalhe, nooweherera avilhelhaka toka ntipashilhe mpaka umalha nlhaalha ipulha vanorupa aya velhaponi.
\v 8 Ni inyu mwaatti nvilhelheke chiicho. Mweemelheke rata chinene munrimani, ukhalhawaya nihuku no uwa Athithi nihaatameria.
\p 
\v 9 Ashilhoko aka, nhitukutuwache mwaashineneru, nhiwe mwaahukumulhiya. Nchuwelheke wiira, mwaanyulha uyo ri vankhorani.
\v 10 Ashilhoko aka mwoopuwelheke anamilhohi oolhumacha nttenga ukhuma wa Athithi, mwooneke chera aya wo uvilhelha mu uhuvihiyani, ni inyu mwaatwariheke yayo etu.
\v 11 Nineehana yayo attu o upuha ukhalhawaya ari o uvilhelha. Nheewa mwaatti uvilhelha wa ashinna Ayubu, nchuwelhaka chenre aya wo upangelhiya ni Athithi wo umalha waya. Ukhalhawaya Athithi phi o rera nrima ni o ikiriri.
\p 
\v 12 Upwaha chonkhaye chiyo, ashilhoko aka, nhilhupelhe vanolheha inyu ittu! Nhilhupelhe wo uromolha irimu mena ilhapo mena ittu ikina iriyoothe. Mwiireke Eiyo, mwathananaka wiira Eiyo. Mwiireke Kihiwe vanothanana inyu wiira Kihiwe. Nhiwe mwaahukumulhiya ni Nlhuku.
\s1 Ulhapelha wo nrima
\p 
\v 13 Yakhalhaka haawo ntu riyoothe nohuva munlhokoni mwinyu, anlhapelheke Nlhuku. Ama yakhalhaka hawo ntu o nrima wo nopuha, yoyo eepeke ichipo cho untotopelha Nlhuku.
\v 14 Chani haawo nreta munlhokoni mwinyu? Yoyo ehaneke ashulhupalhe o nlhoko wa attu anrumelhenlhe Kuristo, awe anlhapelhelha ni unhika makhura wo nchina na Athithi.
\v 15 Ukhalhawaya ulhapelha wo nrima unonlhamiha nreta. Athithi anonhokolhoshera machiri tho nreta uyo, noolhama. Ni vavawo yakhalhaka howonya noohiyereriya uwonya wawe.
\p 
\v 16 Paahi etu nkhoromelhaneke uwonya winyu mwaashineneru, nlhapelhelhaneke wiira nlhamihiye. Ukhalhawaya ulhapelha wo ntu nopanga moombone thoko chinothanana awe Nlhuku uhanaa machiri o upanga chittu chinchi, alhapelhaka wo ukuruvalhelha.
\v 17 Naeliya yaari o makhalhelho anolhikaana thoko hii. Yayo aholhapelha wo ukuruvalhelha wiira ipulha ihirupe, ni iyo khayaarumpe velhaponi wo iyaakha taaru ni nusu.
\v 18 Yamalheke nkayaalhapelha tho, irimu nkayaattukuwa ipulha nkayaarupa, ilhapo nkayaamelha cholhia.
\p 
\v 19 Ashilhoko aka, ntu mmoka arukunuwaka ni uhiya ikeekhene ya Nlhuku ni ntu nkina anhokolhoshaka,
\v 20 nchuwelheke wiira, ntu nonhokolhosha ntu nkina wi ikeekhene ya Nlhuku, nowoopolha ukumi wa yoyo ntu uyo unookhwani ni uhiyereriya uwonya wawe winchi.
